AllowEncodedSlashes NoDecode
ProxyPreserveHost On

ProxyPass        /browser              https://10.0.0.5:9980/browser retry=0
ProxyPassReverse /browser              https://10.0.0.5:9980/browser

ProxyPass        /hosting/discovery    https://10.0.0.5:9980/hosting/discovery retry=0
ProxyPassReverse /hosting/discovery    https://10.0.0.5:9980/hosting/discovery

ProxyPassMatch   "/cool/(.*)/ws$"      wss://10.0.0.5:9980/cool/$1/ws nocanon
ProxyPass        /cool/adminws         wss://10.0.0.5:9980/cool/adminws

ProxyPass        /cool                 https://10.0.0.5:9980/cool
ProxyPassReverse /cool                 https://10.0.0.5:9980/cool

ProxyPass        /hosting/capabilities https://10.0.0.5:9980/hosting/capabilities retry=0
ProxyPassReverse /hosting/capabilities https://10.0.0.5:9980/hosting/capabilities
